This one, I think,
is going to be the progressive electrification

6
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:19.680 position:25% size:50%
of energy demand around the world.

7
00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:23.160 position:25% size:50%
The decade where people will start thinking

8
00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:27.080 position:25% size:50%
