we’ll be developing our strategy
in the next few years.

11
00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.000 position:25% size:50%
The electrification, we see,

12
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.960 position:25% size:50%
is the last step towards a fully sustainable world,

13
00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.520 position:25% size:50%
so a fully decarbonized world.

14
00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:45.840 position:25% size:50%
Electrification means
that there are parts of our economy,

15
00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:50.200 position:25% size:50%
parts of our private life that
will use electricity that before did not.

16
00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:53.560 position:25% size:50%
One big example for us is the great revolution

17
00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:55.720 position:25% size:50%
that is going on for the automotive industry

18
00:00:55.720 --> 00:00:58.960 position:25% size:50%
and all the mobility that will become electrified
in the next ten years,

19
00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:02.120 position:25% size:50%
and to prepare ourselves
for that needs a big investment.

20
00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:04.120 position:25% size:50%
On the other side, we also need to make sure

21
00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:07.400 position:25% size:50%
