24
00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:17.840 position:25% size:50%
It’s the perfect mix
between sustainability and business.

25
00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:25.640 position:25% size:50%
Fighting climate change
is also good for the economy.

26
00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:27.200 position:25% size:50%
So the question is now:

